A comment on Barack Obama’s legacy from below the line in response to Ewen 
MacAskill’s thoughts(see 14:46) 
<https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/live/2017/jan/06/how-can-we-tackle-loneliness-this-year-our-live-look-at-the-week?page=with:block-586e646fe4b081b2b4eda5c0#block-586e646fe4b081b2b4eda5c0>
